title: Lloyd Bridges | Wetbacks (1956) Crime, Drama | Full Length Movie

sources.title: Lloyd Bridges | Wetbacks (1956) Crime, Drama | Full Length Movie
sources.description:
About to lose his sole possession, his boat, for lack of payments, ex- Coast Guardsman Jim Benson takes a gamble on a fishing charter and removes the boat from the dock despite a sheriff's seizure order.
 
Director: Hank McCune
Writer: Edward D. Wood Jr. (as Pete LaRoche)
Stars: Lloyd Bridges, Nancy Gates, Barton MacLane 
Genres: Classics, Cult, Crime, Drama
